ProductInfo.Features:
1 Channel Passive Video Audio and Power Balun Transceiver; Video Transmission via UTP CAT5 Cable
Support all video devices, such as camera, monitor, DVR and DVR card; Compatible with LAN system, using pin 4,5 or pin 7,8.
Outstanding interference rejection and transient protection; Male BNC allows connection directly to the camera or DVR;
10%~20% wire costs saved; Full-motion CCTV video at distances up to 2000ft;
No power required; Lower Cost, Easy Installation.
